

---

## React Vite PWA — Flavor-Specific Notes

### Architecture

React + Vite + Tailwind CSS + PWA. State via Context API + useReducer.

### Layer Rules (Enforced)

- `components/` — UI only, no API calls
- `context/` — State management, coordinates API + UI
- `hooks/` — Custom React hooks
- `utils/` — Pure functions, services (API calls here)
- `types/` — TypeScript definitions
- `constants/` — Config values

See `.github/copilot-design-philosophy.md` for detailed patterns.
See `.github/copilot-security-enforcement.md` for security rules.

### Commands

| Command | Purpose | Speed |
|---------|---------|-------|
| `npm run dev` | Vite dev server with HMR | instant |
| `npm test` | Run tests | ~10s |
| `npm run build:clean` | Clean production build | ~30s |
| `npm run typecheck` | TypeScript strict check | ~5s |

### PWA

Configured via `vite-plugin-pwa` in `vite.config.ts`. Manifest in the plugin config.
Auto-update service worker on new builds.

### Deployment

GitHub Pages via `deploy-pages.yml`. Sets `BASE_URL=/<repo-name>/` for correct asset paths.
